{"tid":1215513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要！！]野餐後睇醫生須知及提防有賤豬出沒","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:48:30.000Z","uid":94137,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ace293f60e0ac25083a9bde10eaf334e36c66f2e","tid":1215513,"uid":94137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"針對好多人因去行山推親扭親腳睇醫生<br />\n又有人因為睇醫生比個別醫療界賤豬出賣<br />\n現有睇醫生指引：<br />\n1. 睇政府急症，可以唔出示身分證，話冇帶，問你number可以唔比，話唔記得左幾多號<br />\n2. 可以要求同醫生單獨對話，唔好係公眾地方講自己野<br />\n每個aed 都有警崗，最近幾日已經有驚係aed 醫生房出面捕住d 人，同醫生傾計講病情唔好講得太深入，甚至可以唔講自己因乜受傷，就算講都留意下出面有冇人偷聽<br />\n3. 可以要求醫生將病情保密，其實驚冇權問醫生or 病人自己既病情，this is about privacy，保護病人私隱係醫療界視為專業守則之一， 唔洗同人透露自己咩事， 亦可以要求醫生唔講（多數都會唔講 不過唔知佢身邊有冇潛在港豬想幫狗）<br />\n<br />\n另外， 收到風有朋友既朋友係QE做<br />\n有人睇醫生既時候，有護士長偷聽到個病人因咩事睇醫生，跟住報串比驚聽，搞到最後病人比人捉左<br />\n但唔知道個位護士長叫咩名，麻煩知道既人可以幫手留言比我地知係邊個仆街<br />\n<br />\n亦麻煩廣大既連登仔，一旦發現左呢d報串精，可以一齊寫信聯署比醫管局投訴佢地， 係醫療界上保護病人私隱係一大守則，呢種出賣病人資料既行為係不被認可，大家投訴係可以制裁到呢種仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：首次出post，有咩1999大家見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145335c1e9395f47cebaf298ad5b0e35f729cd01","tid":1215513,"uid":207291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddfa029686294e94b4d8e2425d1051a228d77e85","tid":1215513,"uid":236140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去私家醫院呀！</span>"},{"pid":"049462bbaf2b95aeb7c3fd3f36d9b87f85468375","tid":1215513,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4f995c3b82e0042d1b6e1ef2836a6f0ff7720ae","tid":1215513,"uid":229695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3dd7fedde6cc22c54e7f511ed1ad14a0d79c356","tid":1215513,"uid":23560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"公立醫院嘅同事工作量都好大<br />\n如果唔係太嚴重嘅可以考慮去私家醫院睇醫生<br />\n減輕佢哋嘅工作量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7218262774c198b20e6c9f359b89b1a589c673","tid":1215513,"uid":220900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"問咗護士朋友<br />\n<br />\n如果求醫，要諗清楚啲問題先答。<br />\n例如你中催淚彈，呼吸困難，就淨係答佢氣管唔舒服，俾刺激性物體整到呼吸困難咁。而你係邊度受傷就冇必要答，佢吹你唔漲。"},{"pid":"aab459ad1e81f717723745e0dbf2788a097a59a9","tid":1215513,"uid":94137,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家就算睇私家都唔好信哂佢地啲人<br />\n要知道當今香港好撚多仆街<br />\n凡事小心<br />\n如果唔係大事就係屋企處理<br />\n大問題既睇下身邊有冇可信既醫護朋友幫手搞搞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2670db533cadea1f6e89cc622b44b347d10d0f3","tid":1215513,"uid":94137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab88627ba2728d9a99bc089e1a97648a7ccd58e","tid":1215513,"uid":94137,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MPMXQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MPMXQy.png&h=b909ff07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d912fc625827efee6a63f2e3e346af8b1cc506","tid":1215513,"uid":94137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b